Class DefaultExpressionEvaluationContext

java.lang.Object
io.micronaut.expressions.context.DefaultExpressionEvaluationContext
All Implemented Interfaces:
ExpressionEvaluationContext, ExtensibleExpressionEvaluationContext
@Internal public class DefaultExpressionEvaluationContext extends Object implements ExtensibleExpressionEvaluationContext
Default implementation of ExtensibleExpressionEvaluationContext. Extending this context will always return new instance instead of modifying the existing one.
Since:
4.0.0
Author:
Sergey Gavrilov
